Harmony Maker
Inspiration creates new realities. Our hands turn form to matter. And harmony takes shape, under the vivid sky of Puglia. 
                          To learn more                        










        Highlights      









Ido sofa
Functionality and style combine in this seating system and matching support surfaces and interior design complements. 
                        Read details                      






La Scala sofa
A classic expression of the best Italian artisan tradition. A masterpiece of skilled craftsmanship, La Scala is a classic Chester sofa with a contemporary flair. 
                        Read details                      






Herman sofa
A harmonious, comprehensive and highly modular seating system, characterized by an external metal support. 
                        Read details                      










        Join the harmony club      




            To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
            supports HTML5 video









United for Harmony
We seek harmony in every moment of life: in our work, in our entertainment, in our relations. We love life, respect for the rules, mistakes that help us do better. And we love doing better. 
                          Join the harmony club                        










