        collection      

        Coffee tables      

Side tables and coffee tables in all shapes and sizes complement Natuzzi Italia living room furniture,in a highly functional interpretation of style.
 







Change view







Typology
Accent tables
Coffee tables
Side tables


























Cabaret


Cabaret is a line of highly versatile coffee tables.









Cabaret X


Cabaret X is a definitely versatile coffee table that hardly goes unnoticed in home or professional environments thanks to its refined minimal design.









Chocolat


Chocolat is a modern coffee table with distinctive geometric shape. The use of fine materials like stone or marble is in line with the latest trends in interior design.









Doris


Doris is an elliptical shaped little table, light in appearance but strong and stable.









Galileo


Galileo is a coffee table that embellishes any environment with a combination of functionality and aesthetics.









Ginger


Ginger is an octagonal shaped little table, light in appearance but strong and stable.









Grace


Grace features a refined curved shape and a beveled edge glass top.









Herman


Created by the Studio Memo designers, the Herman coffee table plays with shapes and sizes, but above all they are the epitome of cutting-edge design and unparalleled comfort.









Ido


Bare cubic elements are arranged horizontally and vertically creating a system of different stories, as to both aesthetics and function.









Kubika


Designed by Pierangelo Sciuto, the Kubika table consists of different elements skillfully combined with refined aesthetic taste.









Labirinto


The Labirinto tables burst with color and geometric shapes in the Natuzzi Italia collection. Designed by architect Claudio Bellini, they combine beauty and functionality in a unique line of interior design products.









Long Beach


Long Beach is an elegant, versatile little table, the ideal complement to your sofa.









Mercurio


Transparency makes the Mercurio coffee table collection elegant and easy to match with different furniture styles.









Meridio


Meridio is a line of versatile coffee tables that can be combined to create unique shapes and volumes, enlivening the living area.









Shanghai


Designed by architect Claudio Bellini, Shanghai is a table that will never fade into the background.









Svevo


Svevo is a line of coffee tables with a distinctly Scandinavian design, also known for its being "different" thanks to the new stylistic research in the creation of new lines.









Tablò


Tablò is a versatile and functional coffee table with a wooden frame and top.









Tempo


The Tempo line of coffee tables is extremely versatile as to available versions and materials that can be combined for a complete and stylish interior design.









Titano


Elegant and refined, the Titano line of coffee tables joins past and present with fine timeless materials, like Dark Emperador marble for the top.









Viavai


Viavai is a line of coffee tables featuring an innovative steel frame and a round top resting on a distinctive three legs design.










